features.text:
Artvatars is a monumental
art collaboration, launched in April 2021, which consist in unique (1/1) NFTs created by 65 elite artists globally. Each one can have up to 12 different components, which were assembled randomly by an AI algorithm. This is the first large-scale art project deployed on Eth-Layer 2 on Polygon (Matic)

Artvatars represents: a disruptive innovation, a schema breaker, an entirely new genre of art, a spectrum of imagery that ranges from the brutally chaotic to the ethereally beautiful, identities with presence and personality, expressions of a collective voice, the hopes, fears and dreams of humanity, inherently multi-faceted reflections of ourselves, entities reunited and reconstructed from fragmentation..  and much more

This project has formed a community with a strong core of art lovers, creatives, and some renowned collectors. This gallery is dedicated to all of them, to the splendid artists and distinguished team that brought Artvatars to life
